        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "skewering one's food with a chopstick in order to pick it up (a breach of etiquette)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「ああ、刺し箸はマナー違反だよ」と母が私を注意した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は無意識のうちに刺し箸をしてしまい、周りの視線に気づいた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "食事の作法として、刺し箸は避けるべき行為とされている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
